1658547483, "title": "微信读书电子书价格为什么比实体书还贵。。。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/867963", "created": 1658462147, "deleted": 0, "content": "非小说\r\n\r\n就一本书，微信读书必须付费卡才能阅读，索性想着买一本回来看得了。微信读书电子书价格 45 元；京东搜实体书，自营 44 元，新人优惠下去 36 元。\r\n\r\n且不说新人优惠价，光原价对比，电子书要 45 而实体书要 44 （还没比较其他平台）。\r\n\r\n有点不太理解，电子书连印刷成本都没有，这个价格为什么可以与实体书齐平甚至还贵一点？", "content_rendered": "<p>非小说</p>\n<p>就一本书，微信读书必须付费卡才能阅读，索性想着买一本回来看得了。微信读书电子书价格 45 元；京东搜实体书，自营 44 元，新人优惠下去 36 元。</p>\n<p>且不说新人优惠价，光原价对比，电子书要 45 而实体书要 44 （还没比较其他平台）。</p>\n<p>有点不太理解，电子书连印刷成本都没有，这个价格为什么可以与实体书齐平甚至还贵一点？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1658462147, "replies": 54, "id": 867963}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 19102, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2226, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 20469, "username": "yanerweb", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yanerweb", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "初级程序员", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/931d/8e8c/20469_mini.png?m=1403855360", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/931d/8e8c/20469_normal.png?m=1403855360", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/931d/8e8c/20469_large.png?m=1403855360", "created": 1336377518, "last_modified": 1403855360}, "last_reply_by": "kyor0", "last_touched": 1658506086, "title": "Apple TV（4K 6 代）可以支持多个遥控器同时使用吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/868033", "created": 1658477062, "deleted": 0, "content": "一个遥控器不够